bio: I am a Content Writer/ Community Builder/Contributor/Researcher
impactDescription:
I have also hosted Twitter Spaces which helped projects understand how they can contribute to and benefit from the Optimism ecosystem.

I have educated lot of people in my region pay much attention to the chain and use majority of Dexes built on the chain.With these activities, users get to contribute and benefit from the ecosystem.

I have taught and 2 of my Telegram members in my community Optimism are active members to the Ambassador Program in the last 7-8 months. 1 of which have successfully obtained the role of ambassador in training.
contributionDescription:
I create educational content about Optimism and ecosystem provide information about new activities and results of previous ones.

Though My main focus is on Twitter(X) communities & Telegram posts. I am  Influencer creating a huge impact: Education/Reviews/AMAs/ Collaborations.

Though my former account on Twitter  @pheyiyex was suspend i still continued share much more content on the New account @custommade_ng .

Lastly, I held a couple of Twitter Spaces as an Optimism ambassador-in-training with projects building and are willing to build on OP to discuss their project and the importance of RetroPGF.
